title: From the Thames to the Trosachs.
author: Thompson, E. H.
snippet: The north transept contains many interesting monuments of England's great men ; among them Pitt, Cobden, Wilberforce,  Newton, Herschel, Keble, the Wesleys, George Canning,  Johnstone, Percival, Fox, Montague, and General Wade.

title: Sparks from a locomotive;
author: Fuller, Hiram
snippet: Lord Palmerston will doubtless succeed Lord Derby; and Cobden and Gibson will be among the elements of the composite Cabinet.
